screen_name: Can’t wait to spend my afternoon on the phone with United Healthcare attempting to understand why their website says they’re paying for testing of COVID-19 but they aren’t paying for all of mine!

I tested positive for COVID and the department of public health was supposed to call me for further instructions. They called me an entire week after testing positive and left a voicemail with no instructions except to call them back.
